*Diši* laganim, dubokim udahima. (Breathe in deeply and slowly.)

*Dišao* je kroz nos. (He was breathing through his nose.)

Kad bi se zatvorio očima, *dišalo* bi mu se pomalo. (When he closed his eyes, he would breathe a little.)

*Diše* li ti? (Are you breathing?)

On je *dišući* počeo da mrmlja. (He started mumbling while breathing.)